{"TopicId":195878,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Cannot use cut \u2702 tool when editing posts","CreatedByName":"catloaf","CreatedById":204108,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-26T05:00:43Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"catloaf","CreatedById":204108,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-26T05:00:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo as everybody knows when you create a quote or other widget you delete it with the cut tool. However when editing post some tools such as cut, some formatting options and other things are missing. I know it\u0027s probably a software limitations but it would be nice to not have\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIgnore this it was a formatting mistake.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nblockquote widget\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204108-catloaf/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022204108\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204108-catloaf/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@catloaf\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204108-catloaf/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022204108\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204108-catloaf/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@catloaf\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0this was a mistake please move along.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is what happens when you don\u0027t know how to end your post...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBtw I\u0027m on mobile right now, can\u0027t test of it happens on pc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-07-26T05:04:58Z\u0022 title=\u002207/26/2020 05:04  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 26, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by catloaf\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EEdit: found workaround, still would be a nice change.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-26T05:37:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have found the best way to get rid of those blocks is to put the cursor immediately before it, and then hit backspace.\u00A0\u00A0 The GUI here is kinda weird and doesn\u0027t always behave as you think it should (try editing a table).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut although, it could just be the mobile interface.\u00A0 I\u0027ve never used the \u0022cut\u0022 tool before.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-26T15:56:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223826249\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022195878\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221595739643\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204108\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022catloaf\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, catloaf said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBtw I\u0027m on mobile right now, can\u0027t test of it happens on pc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHa, I was reading what you were writing and the first thing I thought was, \u0022I bet he\u0027s on mobile.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe forum software works fine on mobile for \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ereading\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E, but when it comes to \u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003Eediting\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E, it\u0027s a bit... flaky. Always has been.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only solution I\u0027ve ever found is to stick to very rudimentary editing when on mobile and don\u0027t quote people (and don\u0027t even get me started about @-pinging and other idiosyncrasies), and save the fancier posts for when I\u0027m on desktop.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"catloaf","CreatedById":204108,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-26T16:00:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is definitely inferior. However, what I don\u0027t understand is why I can do things when creating a post, but\u00A0 cannot do them when editing it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-26T17:11:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223826411\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022195878\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221595779221\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204108\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022catloaf\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, catloaf said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever, what I don\u0027t understand is why I can do things when creating a post, but\u00A0 cannot do them when editing it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause, as I mentioned,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223826409\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022195878\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221595778988\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Snark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Snark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit\u0027s a bit... flaky. Always has been.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Poodmund","CreatedById":128643,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-26T17:52:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, mobile formatting with the WYSIWYG editor sucks. Even when composing a post using the multi-quote feature, you cannot move the quote blocks around and you cannot delete a quote block on mobile by pressing backspace or something sane.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}